text: Omar Zeineddine (; born 13 June 1987) is a Lebanese former professional footballer who played as a midfielder. ==Club career== In 2017, Zeineddine moved to Indonesian club Perseru Serui. ==References== ==External links== * * * Category:1987 births Category:Living people Category:People from North Governorate Category:Lebanese footballers Category:Association football wingers Category:Association football midfielders Category:Riada Wal Adab Club players Category:Lebanese Premier League players Category:Salam Zgharta FC players Category:Lebanese expatriate footballers Category:Expatriate footballers in Indonesia Category:Lebanese expatriate sportspeople in Indonesia Category:Liga 1 (Indonesia) players Category:Perseru Serui players Category:Nejmeh SC players
